(firstQuint)Zolpidem (Myslee) Post Marketing Study in Adolescent Patients With Insomnia - Evaluation With Polysomnography.

 The study consists of two parts.

 All patients will receive placebo in one part and Zolpidem in the other part in a single blind manner.

 Efficacy will be measured with polysomnography .

